{"tid":546841,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"突發-奧巴美揚膝蓋骨受傷","createTime":"2018-02-01T01:21:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T01:31:50.000Z","uid":17641,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"02453832558cce3b449b76a3f5ae6a242716f349","tid":546841,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T01:21:49.000Z","msg":"多蒙特前鋒奧巴美揚周三因傷缺席了加蓬國家隊的世盃外圍賽賽事，起初報道指他是足踝受傷，但「蜜蜂兵團」證實這位射手是膝蓋骨受傷。<br />\n在奧巴美揚倦勤下，加蓬作客意外地0:1不敵莫桑比亞，多蒙特賽後在官方twitter證實，他是因膝蓋骨受傷缺陣，足踝並無任何傷患，但未知將要休息多久。這位今季表現著火的前鋒，在多蒙特20場賽事已勁入22球。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=naB%2FhlqfX3%2Fu6QhLgwQZKP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=490faefc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"9ffa324e596a7ac47b9537bb1c0b0bb157fd51c2","tid":546841,"uid":136738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T01:31:50.000Z","msg":"衲弟今日似乎未食麥克唐衲嘅早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}